      "title": "A toy car is in the fuel line",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A toy car also came to the queue near Trincomalee IOC Linganagar petrol station today.",
        "A small toy car was parked at the car park waiting for fuel.",
        "Other car owners said that a car owner who left this toy car in the car queue until his car was brought has reserved this space."
